wool king
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:a sheepfarmer with a large flock on a large holding.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:sheep king
Pronunciation:
Notes: wool-king
